            "title": "A股低開後向下",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">A股低開後續向下。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬綜指開報3839，跌24點或0.62%，現報3850，跌3點或0.08%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深成指開報13394點，跌51點或0.38%，現報13428，跌13點或0.13%</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300開報4576點，跌17點或0.37%，現報4588，跌5點或0.11%，</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">創業板指數開報3222點，跌13點或0.4%，現報3244，升8點或0.3%。  </p>\n</div>",
